title: Selena Gomez Flaunts Cleavage in Revealing Cut-Out Dress in New York City -- See the Pic!
text: Selena Gomez Flaunts Cleavage in Revealing Cut-Out Dress in New York City -- See the Pic! by Jennifer Drysdale 4:15   Photo: Instagram Selena Gomez is looking good -- and she knows it! The 24-year-old actress looked cool and confident as she flaunted her cleavage in a revealing cut-out dress on Wednesday in New York City. Gomez let the dress speak for itself, sporting minimal makeup and leaving her accessorizes at home. Photo: Star Traks Photo WATCH: Selena Gomez Shares a Selfie From the Day She Was 'Nervous as Hell' Though the singer's dress was flirty and fun, she got serious while discussing her passion project, 13 Reasons Why , during a panel on Wednesday. "I was there for the last episode. I was a mess just seeing it all come to life, because I've experienced just that for sure," shared Gomez, who executive produced the Netflix series. "It hits a very important part of me." "I actually was going through a really difficult time when they started production. I went away for 90 days, and I actually met a ton of kids in this place that were talking about issues that these characters are experiencing," she continued of the show, which centers on a teenager who commits suicide, but leaves behind tapes explaining how her classmates played a role in her death. "It was very confusing for me. I had no idea who I was going to be, what I'm still going to become," she added. "I want to be a part of this, because I think this is what they want, this is what they need." Gomez also appears to be working on new music, sharing a teaser of a new song with fans last week.
